Investor Relations


Impax Asset Management Group plc encourages communication with our shareholders. The main opportunity is at the AGM, normally in February each year, when we give a full presentation on our results and prospects. Shareholders are cordially invited to contact us at other times by phone or e-mail. Within the obvious legal constraints, we will do our best to answer your questions.















