Impax Asset Management Group plc (LSE: IPX) is a specialist asset manager founded in 1998 investing in solutions to resource scarcity (in energy efficiency, alternative energy, water, waste, food and agriculture[7] and related sectors).
Impax Asset Management has been awarded a Queen’s Award for Enterprise: Sustainable Development, the UK’s highest business accolade for business success.[8]
